  "body": "Hi, just checked out the latest implementation of EIP-1559 and found there are 2 related fields in `TransactionArgs` which is `MaxFeePerGas` and `MaxPriorityFeePerGas`. I'm wondering if `MaxFeePerGas` is a required tx arg? since if only `MaxPriorityFeePerGas` is given, `gasPrice` in evm will be zero.\r\n\r\n```\r\nif gasFeeCap.BitLen() > 0 || gasTipCap.BitLen() > 0 {\r\n\tgasPrice = math.BigMin(new(big.Int).Add(gasTipCap, baseFee), gasFeeCap)\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/blob/master/internal/ethapi/transaction_args.go#L214-L216",
